# EmailJS Configuration
# Sign up at https://www.emailjs.com/ and create the following:
#
# 1. Create an Email Service (e.g., Gmail, Outlook, Custom SMTP)
#    - Use sales@automaflow.co.za as the recipient
# 2. Create an Email Template with these variables:
#    - {{from_name}} - Sender's name
#    - {{from_email}} - Sender's email
#    - {{company}} - Sender's company
#    - {{message}} - Message content
#    - {{to_email}} - Set to sales@automaflow.co.za
# 3. Get your Public Key from Account Settings

VITE_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=your_service_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=your_template_id_here
VITE_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=your_public_key_here
